00:47:15,200 --> 00:47:16,220
Haló?

301
00:47:17,550 --> 00:47:18,930
Ahoj, Vier.

302
00:47:20,170 --> 00:47:21,420
To som ja, Sean.

303
00:47:23,200 --> 00:47:24,130
Sean.

304
00:47:24,330 --> 00:47:25,550
Zmenil si si číslo?

305
00:47:27,420 --> 00:47:29,220
Potrebujem zmenu.

306
00:47:30,440 --> 00:47:32,220
