329
00:49:14,770 --> 00:49:16,570
Ako by som mohol?

330
00:49:21,600 --> 00:49:23,130
Ďakujem.

331
00:49:24,840 --> 00:49:26,370
Maj sa.

332
00:49:27,770 --> 00:49:29,170
Ahoj.

333
00:51:00,730 --> 00:51:02,530
Bojím sa, Good.

334
00:51:07,000 --> 00:51:09,170
Bojím sa, že bude mama smutná.

335
00:51:14,820 --> 00:51:15,640
Love.

336
00:51:17,170 --> 00:51:19,240
Čo si myslíš,

337
00:51:20,260 --> 00:51:21,880
čo by zarmútilo našu mamu viac?

338
00:51:21,880 --> 00:51:24,060
To, keby úplne prišla o svoju dcéru,

339
00:51:25,930 --> 00:51:28,150
